### Make user room admin
POST https://{{matrix_url}}/_synapse/admin/v1/rooms/{{matrix_room}}/make_room_admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{matrix_token}}

{
    "user_id": "{{matrix_admin}}"
}

